
[folder structure]
- Docs (documents related to the project)
- Scripts (scripts for the project, e.g. how to start the server)
- node_modules (the npm required libraries to run the project)
- *src (source code for the project)

- LICENSE (the licence for this project)
- README.md (readme for github)
- bs-config.json (browser-sync config file)
- package.json (npm / nodejs project config file)
- tslint.json (typescript code readability tool ???)

########################################################

[src folder structure]
- favicon.ico (icon for the site/ webpage)
- index.html (this page is sort of a starting point to run projectVA, it has 2 buttons bringing you to either the lab mode or the main production mode)
- **main.html (the main production mode, TBD)
- **lab.html (the lab mode, where components are loaded separately, handy for development and testing)
- main.ts (the bootstrap module)
- static (a folder containing statis resources)
  - config (config files related to the components)
  - css (css)
  - img (images)
- systemjs-angular-loader.js (???)
- systemjs.config.extras.js (???)
- systemjs.config.js (configuration for the project, e.g. the source code folder root)
- tsconfig.json (typescript language config
- **va_client (the source / component for the project)

